items.title: Awesome Irc
items.content_text:
### Frameworks / Bridges

*   [dibridge (⭐17)](https://github.com/OpenTTD/dibridge) - Discord ↔ IRC (with puppets) `Python`
*   [Biboumi](https://biboumi.louiz.org/) - IRC gateway for XMPP clients `C`
*   [Heisenbridge (⭐277)](https://github.com/hifi/heisenbridge) - Bouncer-style Matrix IRC bridge `Python`
*   [Appservice-IRC (⭐482)](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-appservice-irc) - Gateway and bridge Matrix ↔ IRC `Javascript`
items.content_html:
Frameworks / Bridges

  • dibridge (⭐17) - Discord ↔ IRC (with puppets) Python
  • Biboumi - IRC gateway for XMPP clients C
  • Heisenbridge (⭐277) - Bouncer-style Matrix IRC bridge Python
  • Appservice-IRC (⭐482) - Gateway and bridge Matrix ↔ IRC Javascript
